text: New school in Sumang, teachers there are from ministry of education and they are well trained. Good future for any students studying there.
Very new and big school. My boy is studying there currently. Have many facilities. Design of the school looks good and modern.

School might be hunted, my friends and I were at the fitness corner exercising and when he went to the toilet we heard him singing but when we reached the singing stoped. We checked all the cubicles and he was no where to be found. When we exit the toilet he mysteriously some how got back out, he told us that he did not see us too and if we were walking to the toilet he would have been obvious if he was walking back. I remembered there was once the toilet was locked up too, to prevent people from going in. Idk why but maybe its cursed.

I went for their open house, seniors there were nice and welcoming and overall the school looks super good and clean. Sadly, I came across something when researching on the school and I'm sad to say that there is no football or volleyball cca  + the DSA also so yea
